	<h2> Music&nbsp; </h2>
			<p> Edmund Buckley writes and records multi-instrumental original music under the name Eddie Bears All, he has written three albums of songs that are currently being recorded as demos at his home.&nbsp; They are Sounds from a Coma, Stone Me and Neurasthenia.&nbsp; Sounds of a Coma is recently completed and the other two will be re recorded soon.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; </p>
			
			
  </aside> 
		
		
		
		
